flac3d>;   * Burgers creep: shear-maxwell = shear-kelvin = the layer ELASTIC G,
flac3d>;     bulk = the layer elastic K  (instantaneous static==creep, no spurious soften).
flac3d>;   * viscosity-maxwell eta_m = 6.0e15 Pa.s ; viscosity-kelvin eta_k = 2.4e13 Pa.s.
flac3d>;   * creep threshold ratio = 0.6 :  q_th = 0.6*(c*cos(phi)+p'*sin(phi)).
flac3d>;   * creep timestep = 600 s (fixed).
